Interface DataConstraint

All Superinterfaces:
IntegrityCheck
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractDataConstraint
public interface DataConstraint
extends IntegrityCheck

Generically represents an integrity check that takes a single Concept and validates some aspect of its content. Checks like DT_M1 are data constraints.
